{"tid":502231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生日前夕要叫分手？","createTime":"2017-12-17T16:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T18:13:23.000Z","uid":151972,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9dde469657fcb42f84a2e252bdec429627dfc801","tid":502231,"uid":151972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"話說女友過幾日生日，咁我就諗住買個蛋糕同佢一齊慶祝，然後就玩足一日，我仲特登唔番工。<br />\n點知到我約佢嗰陣佢又話要溫書，要讀好書，又話對拍拖冇興趣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該點做，唔想咁快放棄呢段感情<br />\n利申：男，蛋糕已落訂，比左訂金"},{"pid":"6f065dd253eb1c664cd866d70ad23a1722951b45","tid":502231,"uid":162696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"咁突然?"},{"pid":"3b1000d81e1d86111972fa35d9cdaf1c39ad2740","tid":502231,"uid":13444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae846e53d14a7844aed40e05fd450f5dd1087161","tid":502231,"uid":36370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"帽事既，照慶祝啦。<br />\n要加多雙筷姐"},{"pid":"b21442f377af23fba3ebb6fbba8eafa8a11887c0","tid":502231,"uid":151972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帽事既，照慶祝啦。<br />\n要加多雙筷姐</blockquote><br />\n如無力挽回要懂得放手"},{"pid":"c26c1a7c539fdda13d744d9d6fad0d2976197163","tid":502231,"uid":151972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁突然?</blockquote><br />\n一個人on99食蛋糕"},{"pid":"8551fddbbac108598499fb2eb0e0e438f5852fac","tid":502231,"uid":151972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"蛋糕仲特登加錢加個牌寫i love u 等的字眼"},{"pid":"38f14e9d247192ce95fd66a6d2caeeb510f9a70e","tid":502231,"uid":162696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"點解對拍拖冇興趣先"},{"pid":"76bf5a258c2ea9fbade5f81ed65